name: Tyson Johnson
description: I’m single with no kids, but hoping to have someday with the right mate. I have been on the sunny coast for over years, but have been busy with work and bringing up my family.. Now its time for me to get a life. I prefer to be out there doing something- whether that is having a coffee or a cold beer! I just need someone to do that with. I’m not interested in playing games nor drama. I just want someone to have fun with either romantically or as a mate
